We’ve fixed a ton of issues this month:

- Made fixes to the 'join group’ function
- Made it easier to place mutiple furni in rooms
- Improved usability of Builder’s Club
PLUS a whole heap of other minor bugs have been exterminated!

- Habbo Staff
